.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-6::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  coach, doctor, entrepreneur, videographer
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: funk, indie, reggae, rock
There 4 different types of food: radish, orange, papaya, raspberry
1. the person eating orange is the coach##1
2. the person eating papaya is the fan of rock##1
3. the coach is on the left of the person eating radish##1
4. the fan of indie is on the left or right of the person eating papaya##3
5. the fan of reggae is on the left or right of the person eating orange##3
6. the entrepreneur is on the left of the person eating raspberry##1
7. the doctor is on the right of the fan of funk##1
8. the doctor is on the left of the fan of rock##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |      3       |      4       |
| Job           | coach    | doctor   | entrepreneur | videographer |
| Music-Genre   | funk     | reggae   | rock         | indie        |
| Food         | orange | radish | papaya         | raspberry       |

