.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-7::.
4 different games are played: scrabble, monopoly, domino, backgammon
The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, dancer, doctor, videographer
There are 4 different nationalities: american, brazilian, japanese, mexican
 1. the brazilian is on the left or right of the american##3
 2. the japanese is on the left or right of the person playing domino##3
 3. the person playing backgammon is on the left or right of the brazilian##3
 4. the doctor is on the right of the japanese##1
 5. the japanese is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
 6. the person playing domino is the person playing domino##1
 7. the doctor is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
 8. the japanese is on the left or right of the videographer##3
 9. the american is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
10. the dancer is on the left or right of the doctor##3
11. the dancer is the japanese##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |     3     |     4     |
| Game         | domino    | scrabble  | monopoly | backgammon   |
| Job           | videographer | dancer   | doctor    | bartender |
| Nationality   | mexican      | japanese | brazilian | american  |

