.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-15::.
There are 4 different nationalities: polish, colombian, indian, dutch
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, hip-hop, punk, trance
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, bike, quad-bike, scooter
1. the fan of blues is on the right of the fan of punk##1
2. the indian is the person driving the airplane##1
3. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
4. the colombian is on the far left or far right##3
5. the polish is the fan of trance##1
6. the dutch is between the polish and the person driving the bike##2
7. the polish is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3     |     4     |
| Nationality          | indian | polish    | dutch | colombian |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop  | trance    | punk      | blues     |
| Transport     | airplane | quad-bike | scooter   | bike      |

