.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-16::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  dancer, entrepreneur, photographer, pilot
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, hiking, baking, drawing
4 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, rat, snake, turtle
1. the pilot is on the left or right of the photographer##3
2. the person who's hobby is baking is on the far left##1
3. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left or right of the owner of the snake##3
4. the owner of the turtle is between the pilot and the person who's hobby is drawing##2
5. the pilot is the person who's hobby is chess##1
6. the owner of the turtle is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is chess##3
7. the owner of the rat is on the far left##1
8. the owner of the rat is on the left or right of the dancer##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |   2    |      3       |     4      |
| Job           | entrepreneur | dancer | photographer | pilot      |
| Hobby   | baking   | drawing | hiking       | chess  |
| Pet           | rat          | snake  | turtle       | guinea-pig |

